casebody.head_matter:
Robert Mitchell JENNINGS, petitioner,
v.
William STEPHENS, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division.
No. 13-7211.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 24, 2014.
Case below, 537 Fed.Appx. 326.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit granted limited to Question 4 presented by the petition.
